                                                      rdfs:range <https://w3id.org/heritagegraph/HeritageAssertion> ;
                                                      rdfs:label "supersedes_assertion" ;
                                                      <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> " Previous version of this assertion (if this is an update). Creates version chain: A1 → A2 → A3 Query pattern: latest assertion = one with no incoming prov:invalidated" ;
                                                      <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <file:/input/CulturalHeritageOntology> .


###  https://w3id.org/heritagegraph/supported_by_institution
